1
00:00:00,510 --> 00:00:08,610
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,777 --> 00:00:17,014
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,253 --> 00:00:19,244
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,258 --> 00:00:26,024
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,095 --> 00:00:29,462
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,665 --> 00:00:33,226
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,602 --> 00:00:36,969
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:44,468
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,547 --> 00:00:53,683
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,756 --> 00:01:01,788
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:02,031 --> 00:01:08,869
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,938 --> 00:01:17,004
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,313 --> 00:01:25,778
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,854 --> 00:01:27,879
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:38,532 --> 00:01:44,471
<i>Hit it or Quit it.</i>
<i>The Final Rounds Get Complicated!</i>

16
00:01:55,228 --> 00:01:55,887
You...

17
00:01:55,962 --> 00:01:57,554
You did it!

18
00:02:01,334 --> 00:02:05,668
<i>So that fox kid can fight like this...</i>

19
00:02:16,182 --> 00:02:17,342
That was awesome!

20
00:02:17,884 --> 00:02:18,714
Well done!

21
00:02:19,486 --> 00:02:20,976
That was a great fight!

22
00:02:32,999 --> 00:02:34,125
Yay!

23
00:02:36,603 --> 00:02:39,367
<i>And he still has the energy</i>
<i>to run around...</i>

24
00:02:39,572 --> 00:02:42,803
<i>Man... He's got crazy stamina that guy...</i>

25
00:02:44,778 --> 00:02:45,972
<i>That Naruto...</i>

26
00:02:46,346 --> 00:02:47,745
<i>He keeps getting stronger...</i>

27
00:02:48,348 --> 00:02:50,043
He did it... that kid.

28
00:02:50,317 --> 00:02:52,547
Yeah! He's on the right track!

29
00:02:53,219 --> 00:02:54,584
And he's a little cute...

30
00:02:57,624 --> 00:02:59,091
<i>Something about it...</i>

31
00:02:59,326 --> 00:03:00,623
<i>I'm envious of you...</i>

32
00:03:01,661 --> 00:03:05,688
<i>Watching your battle makes me think</i>
<i>that I have to work really hard too...</i>

33
00:03:06,366 --> 00:03:07,993
<i>That's amazing, you know?</i>

34
00:03:12,872 --> 00:03:17,104
He won. Is it for real?

35
00:03:17,477 --> 00:03:21,777
I thought he was the same as me,
in the not going anywhere class...

36
00:03:22,282 --> 00:03:23,476
Not going anywhere?

37
00:03:23,783 --> 00:03:25,978
Now people are squealing...

38
00:03:26,052 --> 00:03:27,917
Looks like he's part of the group
that's going somewhere.

39
00:03:28,121 --> 00:03:30,487
Maybe I couldn't beat him...

40
00:03:31,124 --> 00:03:34,491
This is really bad.
It kinda depresses me...

41
00:03:34,661 --> 00:03:38,461
To retain himself and draw out
the Chakras of the Nine-Tailed Fox...

42
00:03:38,565 --> 00:03:42,899
Yeah... Most of the Leaf Village people
here are surprised.

43
00:03:43,903 --> 00:03:45,370
<i>That Naruto...</i>

44
00:03:45,438 --> 00:03:50,034
<i>When did he learn to control the strength</i>
<i>of Nine Tailed Fox to that extent?</i>

45
00:03:56,282 --> 00:03:59,274
Even a bird who gets caught,
once it learns how,

46
00:03:59,352 --> 00:04:02,981
will open the lid of its basket
with its own beak.

47
00:04:07,427 --> 00:04:11,955
He won't give up, for he wants to
fly freely in the sky again.

48
00:04:21,107 --> 00:04:23,405
This time you lost!

49
00:04:32,585 --> 00:04:33,745
<i>Father...</i>

50
00:04:36,122 --> 00:04:38,784
It's okay, there's no damage
to his internal organs.

51
00:04:39,159 --> 00:04:41,855
It seems like his Chakra
is almost used up.

52
00:04:43,563 --> 00:04:47,329
<i>You are not the only one special.</i>

53
00:04:47,700 --> 00:04:50,965
<i>Why do you act against</i>
<i>your fate that much?!</i>

54
00:04:51,538 --> 00:04:55,634
<i>Because I was called a failure...</i>

55
00:04:56,109 --> 00:04:59,704
<i>Those who become Hokage</i>
<i>are born to that fate.</i>

56
00:05:00,180 --> 00:05:02,512
So what?!

57
00:05:07,787 --> 00:05:09,049
Lord Hyuga

58
00:05:11,057 --> 00:05:14,652
I'm sorry but...
Could you step out for a moment?

59
00:05:15,728 --> 00:05:17,491
B-But...

60
00:05:17,664 --> 00:05:19,097
It won't take long.

61
00:05:19,432 --> 00:05:20,490
Y-Yes.

62
00:05:31,511 --> 00:05:33,342
What do you need from me?

63
00:05:34,280 --> 00:05:35,577
That day...

64
00:05:37,450 --> 00:05:40,544
I came to tell you the truth...
about that day.

65
00:05:41,754 --> 00:05:42,948
That day...?

66
00:06:10,984 --> 00:06:15,114
At that time, I intended to die!

67
00:06:17,857 --> 00:06:20,291
W-What are you talking about?!

68
00:06:20,793 --> 00:06:22,385
That day my father...

69
00:06:22,462 --> 00:06:24,828
He was killed
as your body double!

70
00:06:34,140 --> 00:06:37,598
The truth of that day... is here.

71
00:06:39,112 --> 00:06:44,140
They're probably only excuses made
at the convenience of the head family.

72
00:06:44,918 --> 00:06:48,854
The person you are now...
should be able to understand.

73
00:06:55,728 --> 00:06:56,717
This writing...!

74
00:07:03,403 --> 00:07:08,397
Neji... I only have a little time left.

75
00:07:09,542 --> 00:07:13,945
I want to use that limited time
to convey something to you...

76
00:07:14,514 --> 00:07:16,141
<i>Convey something to me?</i>

77
00:07:19,452 --> 00:07:21,386
The head of Ninjas from the
Land of Lightning,

78
00:07:21,454 --> 00:07:25,515
who was trying to kidnap Miss Hinata,
was killed by Lord Hiashi...

79
00:07:26,059 --> 00:07:30,996
But the Land of Lightning didn't
acknowledge the abduction of Miss Hinata,

80
00:07:31,064 --> 00:07:33,965
made only the killing
of the head Ninja a problem,

81
00:07:34,033 --> 00:07:36,433
and made unreasonable demands.

82
00:07:39,172 --> 00:07:40,764
It can't be helped.

83
00:07:41,007 --> 00:07:44,499
With my one life,
the village can be saved...

84
00:07:46,312 --> 00:07:49,713
Wait, Hiashi. Don't be so hasty!

85
00:07:51,217 --> 00:07:56,314
The Hyuga's Kekkei Genkai
is an important strength of this land.

86
00:07:56,689 --> 00:08:00,921
It is the duty of the head family
to protect it forever...

87
00:08:00,994 --> 00:08:03,588
However, for the sake of that duty...

88
00:08:03,663 --> 00:08:07,121
if we involve our land
in a desperate war...!

89
00:08:07,467 --> 00:08:10,698
I understand that!
That's why...

90
00:08:12,171 --> 00:08:15,038
Isn't that why
we have branch families?

91
00:08:16,175 --> 00:08:20,908
Hizashi's corpse...
We'll hand it over as your body double.

92
00:08:22,615 --> 00:08:26,346
Hizashi too...
understands the situation.

93
00:08:32,558 --> 00:08:37,495
However, what they want is
the secret of the power of the Byakugan.

94
00:08:38,931 --> 00:08:41,195
The point in time that
Hizashi becomes a corpse,

95
00:08:41,267 --> 00:08:43,531
that power will be sealed.

96
00:08:44,337 --> 00:08:47,238
I don't believe that the Land of Lightning
will consent to that.

97
00:08:48,941 --> 00:08:51,205
That's their true intent,

98
00:08:51,277 --> 00:08:58,206
but the condition made by Lightning is to
"Hand over Hiashi Hyuga's dead body."

99
00:08:58,718 --> 00:09:00,743
We pretend that we agreed
to their terms,

100
00:09:00,820 --> 00:09:04,517
and hand Hizashi,
who is identical to you, over...

101
00:09:04,590 --> 00:09:07,457
and they can't pursue it
any further than that.

102
00:09:07,794 --> 00:09:09,557
B-But...

103
00:09:13,132 --> 00:09:16,795
Hiashi... The time has come...

104
00:09:17,270 --> 00:09:21,468
Your predecessors have done the same
to protect the power of Hyuga clan.

105
00:09:22,608 --> 00:09:26,874
Even siblings...
have the heart to write each other off.

106
00:09:29,148 --> 00:09:33,710
That is the fate of the head family.

107
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:39,285
And this... is the destiny of
ones born into Hyuga!

108
00:09:41,427 --> 00:09:44,760
Where has Lord Hiashi,
who is always bullish, go?

109
00:09:45,565 --> 00:09:48,466
The scale of this issue is different
from the ones in the past!

110
00:09:48,901 --> 00:09:49,959
It's not that easy...

111
00:10:00,046 --> 00:10:04,346
H-Hizashi... you...

112
00:10:04,751 --> 00:10:07,447
Please... let me go

113
00:10:10,923 --> 00:10:16,293
You... You... have Neji.

114
00:10:16,963 --> 00:10:20,763
Why do you choose death...
for the head family?!

115
00:10:21,467 --> 00:10:22,661
That's not so!

116
00:10:25,404 --> 00:10:27,998
I have been resenting
the head family.

117
00:10:28,608 --> 00:10:31,076
To tell the truth
even now I'm bitter.

118
00:10:31,511 --> 00:10:33,035
That's why...

119
00:10:33,513 --> 00:10:40,248
I want to die protecting you as
"my brother," not as the head family.

120
00:10:41,387 --> 00:10:47,383
It's the first time I've had
the freedom to choose.

121
00:10:48,895 --> 00:10:53,195
I've only shown Neji my ugly side.

122
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:59,131
However, now I've come here
and finally know my own intentions.

123
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:04,403
So please tell Neji...

124
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:09,243
I-I wasn't killed to protect
the head family...

125
00:11:09,382 --> 00:11:14,581
but to protect my siblings,
family and the land...

126
00:11:14,654 --> 00:11:17,817
by my own will I chose death!

127
00:11:25,031 --> 00:11:30,367
T-To choose death...
you call that freedom...?

128
00:11:32,271 --> 00:11:33,568
Big brother...

129
00:11:34,373 --> 00:11:39,572
Once, just this once,
I wanted to defy the fate of Hyuga.

130
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:43,271
I wanted to choose my own fate.

131
00:11:44,584 --> 00:11:46,074
That's all.

132
00:11:50,456 --> 00:11:53,220
<i>Overcome your own fate, Neji...</i>

133
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:58,294
<i>Fate is something you work out</i>
<i>with your own hands.</i>

134
00:11:59,232 --> 00:12:00,392
Father...

135
00:12:03,169 --> 00:12:05,399
This is... the truth!

136
00:12:08,274 --> 00:12:09,798
I'm sorry!

137
00:12:18,651 --> 00:12:22,280
Please... raise your head.

138
00:12:33,633 --> 00:12:34,463
<i>Father...</i>

139
00:12:35,268 --> 00:12:42,037
<i>I wonder if a person's destiny is</i>
<i>only floating like a cloud in a fixed current...</i>

140
00:12:42,742 --> 00:12:47,406
<i>Or is a person able to ride</i>
<i>on the current that he chooses.</i>

141
00:12:48,047 --> 00:12:49,844
<i>I don't understand it well yet.</i>

142
00:12:50,416 --> 00:12:53,817
<i>Whichever, the end point</i>
<i>might still be the same...</i>

143
00:12:54,587 --> 00:12:57,021
<i>Just, when the choice is the latter...</i>

144
00:12:57,189 --> 00:12:59,817
<i>people turn toward the goal of</i>
<i>living and work hard toward it.</i>

145
00:12:59,992 --> 00:13:03,484
<i>And those who hold that</i>
<i>are really strong.</i>

146
00:13:04,096 --> 00:13:06,758
<i>I feel like I finally understand,</i>
<i>through this battle...</i>

147
00:13:09,035 --> 00:13:10,730
<i>And... father...</i>

148
00:13:11,370 --> 00:13:13,463
<i>I have only one goal...</i>

149
00:13:15,041 --> 00:13:18,533
<i>I want to become stronger,</i>
<i>so I won't lose to anyone.</i>

150
00:13:20,780 --> 00:13:22,509
<i>That's how I feel now.</i>

151
00:13:24,317 --> 00:13:30,153
<i>Father...I see many birds flying.</i>
<i>And they seem to be enjoying themselves.</i>

152
00:13:41,034 --> 00:13:42,501
It's buzzing.

153
00:13:42,569 --> 00:13:44,935
That's because it was a good battle...

154
00:13:46,006 --> 00:13:48,702
Certainly, there's that too, but...

155
00:13:50,110 --> 00:13:56,447
It's likely that, for the curious heads
of Ninja and the feudal lords,

156
00:13:56,516 --> 00:13:59,747
there is no match they look forward to
more than this next match.

157
00:14:02,956 --> 00:14:07,655
By the way, it seems that
he wasn't seen at the opening ceremony...

158
00:14:08,061 --> 00:14:10,495
He's arrived here already, hasn't he?

159
00:14:15,168 --> 00:14:17,432
There's been no news of Sasuke.

160
00:14:17,937 --> 00:14:19,598
And there's the issue of Orochimaru.

161
00:14:20,373 --> 00:14:22,739
Before everyone starts to make noise,
we should disqualify him...

162
00:14:26,613 --> 00:14:30,344
What's going on?!
Hurry up and start the next match!

163
00:14:30,417 --> 00:14:32,180
How long are you going to
make us wait!

164
00:14:32,252 --> 00:14:33,742
Before night falls!

165
00:14:35,622 --> 00:14:38,785
I wonder what's going on
with the next match?

166
00:14:38,858 --> 00:14:40,689
Is Sasuke here?

167
00:14:42,362 --> 00:14:43,454
<i>Sasuke...</i>

168
00:14:44,531 --> 00:14:48,228
That guy...
What in the world is he doing?!

169
00:14:48,668 --> 00:14:49,862
Is he planning
not to show up?

170
00:14:50,904 --> 00:14:53,634
A wise man never courts danger...

171
00:14:54,307 --> 00:14:55,638
A wise judgement... is it?

172
00:15:00,914 --> 00:15:02,575
What are you saying?

173
00:15:03,183 --> 00:15:06,584
He'll definitely come! Believe it!

174
00:15:19,065 --> 00:15:22,557
<i>But seriously, what is he doing?</i>

175
00:15:22,836 --> 00:15:26,169
<i>Keep this up and he...</i>
<i>he'll be disqualified.</i>

176
00:15:27,707 --> 00:15:29,140
There's no choice...

177
00:15:30,944 --> 00:15:33,742
Sasuke is... disqualified.

178
00:15:33,847 --> 00:15:34,506
Yes.

179
00:15:35,115 --> 00:15:37,845
Sasuke Uchiha is... disqualified?

180
00:15:38,685 --> 00:15:41,153
It has to be done.

181
00:15:43,423 --> 00:15:45,084
What in the world are
we going to do?

182
00:15:45,325 --> 00:15:47,919
If that guy doesn't show up,
our plan of strategy...

183
00:15:48,194 --> 00:15:49,786
This isn't good...

184
00:15:53,800 --> 00:15:55,563
Could he have...?

185
00:15:56,970 --> 00:15:59,131
<i>Where are you going, Gaara?</i>

186
00:16:00,540 --> 00:16:03,270
<i>I'm going to confirm my existence...</i>

187
00:16:04,077 --> 00:16:06,341
<i>Darn that Gaara...</i>

188
00:16:06,980 --> 00:16:08,971
<i>I wonder if he really killed him...</i>

189
00:16:19,426 --> 00:16:21,417
Sasuke one more time...

190
00:16:24,831 --> 00:16:25,729
What happened?

191
00:16:26,566 --> 00:16:29,694
It's obvious that you're there
standing with the thirst for blood.

192
00:16:29,769 --> 00:16:31,259
Why don't you come out?

193
00:16:37,777 --> 00:16:39,108
It's you...

194
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:48,582
Lord Hokage...

195
00:16:48,822 --> 00:16:52,622
I want you to consider waiting a little bit
for Sasuke Uchiha's disqualification.

196
00:16:54,461 --> 00:16:55,894
I understand your point, but...

197
00:16:56,262 --> 00:16:59,129
No matter how excellent the Shinobi,

198
00:16:59,199 --> 00:17:01,997
to make light of time is not
a qualification for Chunin.

199
00:17:02,435 --> 00:17:04,733
If there's no clear reason to satisfy

200
00:17:04,804 --> 00:17:07,932
the heads of Ninja and feudal lords
who are here,

201
00:17:08,007 --> 00:17:09,872
there's no reason to wait for him!

202
00:17:12,111 --> 00:17:13,544
I see...

203
00:17:14,647 --> 00:17:16,945
Well then, there is a sufficient reason.

204
00:17:18,751 --> 00:17:20,480
Including myself...

205
00:17:20,553 --> 00:17:23,716
most of the heads of Ninja and
feudal lords that are here...

206
00:17:23,790 --> 00:17:27,351
came here because
they want to see the next match.

207
00:17:30,964 --> 00:17:31,760
However...

208
00:17:32,098 --> 00:17:35,659
He's the remaining survivor
of the "Uchiha."

209
00:17:35,735 --> 00:17:40,570
Land of the Wind too, absolutely,
is hoping for a bout with our Gaara.

210
00:17:42,642 --> 00:17:43,472
Lord Hokage...

211
00:17:44,811 --> 00:17:48,008
<i>There's no guarantee that</i>
<i>Sasuke will come but...</i>

212
00:17:49,516 --> 00:17:50,915
All right then...

213
00:17:51,784 --> 00:17:55,777
We shall specially postpone
this match and wait.

214
00:17:58,291 --> 00:18:00,782
Lord Hokage! Really...

215
00:18:01,661 --> 00:18:03,219
Inform so to the Proctor!

216
00:18:03,663 --> 00:18:05,494
Y-Yes.

217
00:18:08,868 --> 00:18:09,835
However...

218
00:18:10,203 --> 00:18:14,469
It's rare for you to insist like that,
Lord Kazekage.

219
00:18:15,041 --> 00:18:16,201
Well...

220
00:18:16,409 --> 00:18:19,901
To show off the Shinobi's qualities
of our village to the feudal lords...

221
00:18:19,979 --> 00:18:22,504
there's no better opponent
than an Uchiha.

222
00:18:23,483 --> 00:18:25,713
It's a chance for us as well.

223
00:18:26,052 --> 00:18:28,350
C'mon, what happened to the match?!

224
00:18:29,322 --> 00:18:30,983
What happened to Uchiha?!

225
00:18:33,026 --> 00:18:34,186
I understand...

226
00:18:37,864 --> 00:18:43,564
Everyone! The candidate for the
next battle has not arrived here!

227
00:18:43,903 --> 00:18:49,500
We'll briefly postpone this battle
and start the following battle ahead of it.

228
00:18:52,312 --> 00:18:55,042
What is he doing... that Sasuke?

229
00:18:55,248 --> 00:18:59,116
Great, so Sasuke didn't get disqualified!

230
00:19:05,124 --> 00:19:06,216
That's good...

231
00:19:06,559 --> 00:19:11,155
Hey! That means my match
is one match closer!

232
00:19:12,432 --> 00:19:14,366
Then, on to the next pair!

233
00:19:14,834 --> 00:19:17,928
Kankuro and Shino Aburame!
Come down!

234
00:19:20,573 --> 00:19:23,406
<i>My match...doesn't matter at all.</i>

235
00:19:26,980 --> 00:19:28,106
<i>More importantly...</i>

236
00:19:28,181 --> 00:19:34,211
<i>I'd rather not expose the Mechanism</i>
<i>of Crow to the enemy before the plan...</i>

237
00:19:37,090 --> 00:19:38,022
Proctor!

238
00:19:38,458 --> 00:19:39,686
I abstain!

239
